# TWRP Device Tree for ZTE Changxing 50 (P720S16)

## Device specifications

| Feature                 | Specification                                              |
| ----------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------- |
| Chipset                 | Unisoc T760 (UMS9620)                                      |
| CPU                     | Octa-core (4x2.2 GHz Cortex-A76 + 4x2.0 GHz Cortex-A55)  |
| GPU                     | Mali-G57                                                   |
| Memory                  | 4GB / 6GB RAM                                              |
| Storage                 | 128GB (eMMC)                                               |
| SIM                     | Dual Nano-SIM                                              |
| MicroSD                 | Up to 1TB                                                  |
| Battery                 | 4000 mAh, non-removable                                    |
| Charging                | 5W standard charging                                       |
| Display                 | 6.52 inch, 720x1600 (HD+), IPS LCD, 90Hz                 |
| Rear Camera             | 13 MP, AF, LED flash                                       |
| Front Camera            | 5 MP                                                       |
| 3.5mm jack              | Yes                                                        |
| OS                      | Android 13 (MyOS 13)                                       |
| Fingerprint             | No                                                         |

## Device picture

![ZTE Changxing 50](https://oss.ztedevices.com/prod/cn/2023/09/20230920458.jpg)

## Features

**Works:**
- [x] ADB
- [x] Decryption (Android 13)
- [x] Screen brightness
- [x] MTP
- [x] Flashing (zip/img)
- [x] Backup/Restore
- [x] USB OTG

**Not works:**
- [ ] Fastbootd (if applicable)
- [ ] Vendor partition backup (size limit)

**Untested:**
- [ ] Vibration

## Compile

First checkout minimal twrp with aosp tree:

```bash
repo init -u https://github.com/minimal-manifest-twrp/platform_manifest_twrp_aosp.git -b twrp-12.1
repo sync
```

Then add these projects to `.repo/local_manifests/roomservice.xml`:

```xml
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<manifest>
  <project name="android_device_zte_P720S16" path="device/zte/P720S16" remote="github" revision="twrp-12.1" />
</manifest>
```

Now you can sync the sources:

```bash
repo sync
```

To build:

```bash
source build/envsetup.sh
lunch twrp_P720S16-eng
mka recoveryimage
```

## Thanks

- [TeamWin Recovery Project](https://github.com/teamwin)
